citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 9:30am on 30-Aug-
2023. We made contact with a facility representative at about 9:30am. The person we spoke with said a representative
would not be available for an inspection and that the licensee would be gone in the morning and wouldn't be available for
the rest of the day.
Additional Inspectors:
KIMBERLY MILLER, ANIMAL CARE INSPECTOREnd Section
